Ghanaian actor, John Dumelo took a stylish shade at his wife, Gifty Mawunya, while celebrating her birthday today.  The actor-turned-politician shared a lovely picture of himself posing with his wife raising her leg in the image and then wrote:  “Dunno why women always raise one leg when taking pictures but Nways happy birthday @missgeeonly. Thanks for everything and may God bless you abundantly. Thanks for being a wonderful mother and wife.”  <img class="img-responsive text-center lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://i2.wp.com/goldennewsng.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/758b23b63f917b210d46a836164e14bd.png?w=696&amp;ssl=1" alt='"Dunno why women always raise one leg when taking pictures"- Ghanaian actor, John Dumelo hilariously shades his wife on her birthday?' border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" data-cfstyle="margin: auto;border:0px solid black; height:314px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; width:500px" data-cfsrc="https://i2.wp.com/goldennewsng.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/758b23b63f917b210d46a836164e14bd.png?w=696&amp;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1"><img class="img-responsive text-center lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i2.wp.com/goldennewsng.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/758b23b63f917b210d46a836164e14bd.png?w=696&amp;ssl=1" alt="&quot;Dunno why women always raise one leg when taking pictures&quot;- Ghanaian actor, John Dumelo hilariously shades his wife on her birthday?" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" data-cfstyle="margin: auto;border:0px solid black; height:314px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; width:500px" data-cfsrc="https://i2.wp.com/goldennewsng.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/758b23b63f917b210d46a836164e14bd.png?w=696&amp;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i2.wp.com/goldennewsng.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/758b23b63f917b210d46a836164e14bd.png?w=696&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" 